<br>
What im asking is when I should start getting some resist gear? As of now I have no resist gear and 160 int, should I get more int items or go for some resist gear? Any advice on some quests to do because Í only have 200 plat in the bank? I like doing quests but im having a hard time finding any to do because of my faction ( Bertoxxulous caster )<br>
<br>
Sidenote: Is it just me or is it quite easy to snare yourself and the mob with bonds of force? Have done this more times then I can count =)<br>
