<br>
From what I know, it is quite easy to snare yourself when quadding, as it is an AE. And while your resists will keep that from happening, I personally would recommend getting more INT gear at this point if your intelligence is at 160 currently and you can only get one or the other. I am not a wizard, so someone else my tell you differently, but speaking as a caster, intelligence gear will help you more overall.<br>
<br>
As far as obtaining resist gear, I acquired mine over time. I am 53 and have a pretty decent amount of resist gear which has served me pretty well. I would say to keep your eyes open for good deals in the bazaar and get it little by little. <p><center>
